thread.title: Terry

author: Terry
title: Terry
text: We made a last-minute decision to buy tickets for the James Taylor concert at Rod Laver Arena and used the Ticketmaster Resale site for the first time. I was surprised to find that the tickets we purchased were actually cheaper than the face value of the ticket ($115 compared to $144). The whole process was seamless and the tickets arrived in plenty of time to print out and take to the concert which we loved. More than happy with the experience and would recommend to our friends.
